'''圣弥额尔总领天使堂'''（Chiesa di San Michele Arcangelo）位于[[意大利|意大利]][[卡普里岛|卡普里岛]][[阿纳卡普里|阿纳卡普里]]的圣尼各老广场，建于1719年，八角形，[[巴洛克|巴洛克]]风格<ref name="FisherWang2007">{{cite book|last1=Fisher|first1=Robert I. C.|last2=Wang|first2=Amy|title=Fodor's Naples, Capri & the Amalfi Coast|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=zUqAh9xFa5UC&pg=PA219|accessdate=5 July 2012|date=6 March 2007|publisher=Random House Digital, Inc.|isbn=978-1-4000-1743-0|pages=219–}}</ref>。该堂由于其著名的陶器[[镶嵌艺术|镶嵌艺术]]而获得文物古迹称号<ref name="umuc.edu">{{cite web|url=http://ac-support.europe.umuc.edu/~jmatthew/naples/sanmichele.htm|title=The Church of San Michele (Capri-Anacapri)|publisher=University of Maryland University College|accessdate=6 July 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120902082811/http://ac-support.europe.umuc.edu/~jmatthew/naples/sanmichele.htm|archivedate=2012年9月2日}}</ref>。

